{"tid":1644185,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"留意 班狗係可以要求除口罩","createTime":"2019-10-10T12:49:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T13:24:06.000Z","uid":55083,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3033aebcfe4d97b1ed9d4dff0aef05489b5db6b8","tid":1644185,"uid":55083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T12:49:12.000Z","msg":"頭先尖咀碼頭 黃/王生講遊行先可以要你除係錯<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap241K\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elegislation.gov.hk%2Fhk%2Fcap241K&d=qlseXWlRX%2BAJHWkEdqgF5UZZ0ArqIWVBMBEeODt8eII%3D&h=2bc52ad1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap241K</a><br />\n根據241K章第5條:<br />\n5.有權要求於公眾地方除去蒙面物品<br />\n(1)如身處公眾地方的人正在使用蒙面物品，而某警務人員合理地相信，該蒙面物品相當可能阻止識辨身分，則本條就該人而適用。<br />\n(2)上述警務人員可 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n(a)截停上述的人，並要求該人除去有關蒙面物品，以令該警務人員能夠核實該人的身分；及<br />\n(b)如該人沒有遵從(a)段所指的要求&mdash;&mdash;除去該蒙面物品。<br />\n(3)任何人沒有遵從第(2)(a)款所指的要求，即屬犯罪，一經定罪，可處第3級罰款及監禁6個月。<br />\n所以佢只係好彩撞正班狗都唔清楚條例<br />\n如果以後撞到呢個狀況唯有啃咗佢<br />\n唔係可以即拉"},{"pid":"f8f34cd29cd4798e8773f0fd7cedfcb9c5aa35a3","tid":1644185,"uid":55083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T12:53:09.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4157ddbfe577aeba0f0ac6ac2821ed12df6a12db","tid":1644185,"uid":55083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T12:54:30.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"36cf45cae36b34fb409c03633b09ce9c65fdeca0","tid":1644185,"uid":55083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T12:57:30.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"453ca0199b62a6a781c2a51ad98fb5937149446d","tid":1644185,"uid":55083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T13:00:53.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2d243adc3d0a389f1cb0cbc58bd0cd3b711e1c7b","tid":1644185,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T13:01:13.000Z","msg":"我係商場係私人地方"},{"pid":"4bd5666f16b54e27dc9628a95724d2f4aa3ded1a","tid":1644185,"uid":55083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"sco